nodes.caption: I have been able to take 15 vacations since Aug 2015...on top of my few hundred a month, I have paid off an additional 5k in student loans, i have been able to let my wife be a stay at home mom....im not saying this to boast, in fact just the opposite.. I'm not Special. If i can do this you can do this! I didn't graduate college...if I can do this you can do this! I am the  father of 2, husband to 1 if I can do this you can do this. I am a full time employee...if I can do this you can do this. I had every excuse available, no time, too busy, got kids, can't afford it, don't know how, I never done this before, I don't think it's for me! The only thing that has allowed me to have the #Results I have had is simple, I didn't take those excuses, instead I paid attention to people worth paying attention to. People who could afford the lifestyle I wanted for me and my family.. I know #SuccessLeaveClues. I saw an #opportunity instead of an #obstacle. I had #fear, but I have #faith which gave me #courage to act on what I saw...i made a #decision which led me to a #commitment to continue my #actions regardless of naysayers, regardless of rejection, regardless of my circumstances. ..#Regardless! Now all I want to do is help people like YOU do the same thing... because I believe you can do it too! Only question... are you ready to get started or will you let doubt, fear, and excuses hold you back? #TheHustleWillMakeTheDreamTheReality #TeamThrottle #LetsGetIt #JoinTheMovement

Feliz comienzo de semana mi gente.. no olviden esto, cada día es un nuevo comienzo, una nueva oportunidad para muchas cosas!!! Recuerda.. tienes que andar y crear el camino andando.. no encontrarás un camino ya hecho. No es barato alcanzar lo que tanto quieres y deseas.. todo tiene su trabajo y sacrificio.. Tendrás que crear el camino andando tu solo.. siendo TU.. tu propia motivación.. el camino no esta ya hecho esperándote.. Es justo como el cielo, los pájaros vuelan pero no dejan huellas.. No los puedes seguir.. no hay huellas detrás! Se tu el que cree el camino y de el ejemplo! Cuando tú quieres tú puedes, solo tienes que dar el primer paso!!!.. caminando, corriendo.. pero dalo🏄🏼‍♀️✨🙏🏻❤
